{"tid":31835,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大亞灣泄漏，第三日始封","createTime":"2016-12-10T01:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T01:29:02.000Z","uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd0caae095424f9ec7f82d13bb939abacac45de","tid":31835,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284#sthash.rIlWVfnY.5xRyvyw3.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284%23sthash.rIlWVfnY.5xRyvyw3.dpuf&d=7zuk36%2BAJRB7bt8ZW%2Ff2xn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=fef9bacf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284%23sthash.rIlWVfnY.5xRyvyw3.dpuf&h=81257ac2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284#sthash.rIlWVfnY.5xRyvyw3.dpuf</a><br />\n明報專訊】內地微信公號「中國核能」透露，廣東大亞灣核電站上月底大修期間發生主泵阻尼器泄漏事件，隨後在廣核設計院核島所牽頭下，陝西特種橡膠製品公司承擔封堵項目。該公司在接到任務幾小時內設計出密封方案，並通過國家核安全局批准，2日內完成工裝模具製造、電器控制系統改造、膠圈生產，第3日一行3人將所有封堵工具送往大亞灣基地，密封設備於上周二（11月29日）完成安裝，周日（4日）並網發電。據悉，現場操作環境有放射性。目前，陝西特種橡膠製品公司發布的有關消息已被刪除，大亞灣網站並無披露這一事件。 - See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284#sthash.rIlWVfnY.IQ9IB26C.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284%23sthash.rIlWVfnY.IQ9IB26C.dpuf&d=7zuk36%2BAJRB7bt8ZW%2Ff2xn8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=fe85bc54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284%23sthash.rIlWVfnY.IQ9IB26C.dpuf&h=a0d75692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284#sthash.rIlWVfnY.IQ9IB26C.dpuf</a><br />\n<br />\n用橡膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a0b82c0bc2ab6065b49d6b90a47b9c4a863b93","tid":31835,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/10/092901_cf97de2e8c854ed5ec14bf2cf4e8b6e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F10%2F092901_cf97de2e8c854ed5ec14bf2cf4e8b6e0.jpg&h=d4433f05&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}